ica!\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1540, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998897411168258, \"rank\": 0.00010799137843288269, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Native_Americans_in_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the United States\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cue the racism and misogyny.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cue\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"the racism\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"misogyny\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never mind she's a Baptist, a Christian, a lifelong public servant.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 0.9790338702261326, \"rank\": 0.02140486000940716, \"text\": \"Baptist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999933091704507, \"rank\": 6.690874199898789e-06, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lifelong public servant\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, JD Vance may soon learn that crossing chi