"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Converse sneakers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chuck_Taylor_All-Stars\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"insurrection\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"a tweet\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as for drag queens in Paris, if some of these folks actually bothered to study history, they'd learn there is a rich tradition of sacred clowns whose role is to make fun of our most sacred traditions so we do not take ourselves too seriously.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999972484262456, \"rank\": 2.7515812024363645e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"these folks\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"a rich tradition\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"sacred clowns\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"whose role\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"our most sacred traditions\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, if they bothered to read the Bible with a little more scholarship at hand, they'd also discover that, at points, it's hilarious, and Jesus himself was not above cracking jokes and using a little well-timed sarcasm.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Bible\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"a little more scholarship\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"jokes\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"a little well-timed sarcasm\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be the first to admit this pieceis a bit snarkier than most of my pleas for sanity and good will among Christians, but I am finding it exasperating and hard to take seriously all the pearl-clutching, defensiveness, hypocrisy and meanness of people who call themselves Christians and act anything but Christ-like.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this pieceis\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"my pleas\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"sanity\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"good will\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"hypocrisy\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"meanness\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They give the rest of us a bad name.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad name\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surely, there are more important things for Christians to do in the world than worry about drag queens, although you would not know that from the legislation in a number of red states.\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more important things\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"the legislation\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"red states\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What if Christians spent their timeactually doing the things Jesus said God's people ought to do, like feeding the hungry, clothing the naked, making peace and loving our neighbors?\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031179790205, \"rank\": 9.689136437975761e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3163, \"end\": 3168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"God's people\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"our neighbors\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know we progressives have to take the pearl-clutchers seriously, though, because we have seen what they do when they are in power.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pearl-clutchers\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Project 2025 lays out such a dystopian vision thatThe Handmaid's Taleseems child's play.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Project\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3425}, {\"ngram\": \"such a dystopian vision\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"Handmaid's Taleseems child's play\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a process theologian, I believe God is at work in every particle of the universe, calling it to achieve its divine aim, and so we can not give up on those who clutch their pearls and often throw them before swine.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a process theologian\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3546}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"every particle\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"the universe\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"its divine aim\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"their pearls\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"swine\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we can not simply call them out.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Black feminist activist Loretta Ross says, we have to call them in.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3789, \"end\": 3801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Loretta Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loretta_Ross\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The stakes are too high for us tosit on the sidelines.\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The stakes\", \"from\": 3834, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to speak the truth.\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two plus two does not equal five.\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The emperor has no clothes.\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The emperor\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"no clothes\", \"from\": 3967, \"to\": 3977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And drag queens at the Last Supper are not a threat to Christianity.\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 4047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4034, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 4.821257331944368e-12, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump, however, is, and he has already dragged down a large swath of evangelicals into his cult.\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a large swath\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"evangelicals\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"his cult\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now is not the time to clutch pearls.\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4165}, {\"ngram\": \"pearls\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I imagine Jesus would have had a good laugh with the drag queens.\", \"from\": 4185, \"to\": 4250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4195, \"end\": 4200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999159758808, \"rank\": 8.402430618153063e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good laugh\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"the drag queens\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, keep in mind, when he had his chance to amass political power, he did not make a deal with the devil.\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"his chance\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"political power\", \"from\": 4316, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"a deal\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4355}, {\"ngram\": \"the devil\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Susan M. Shawis professor of women, gender and sexuality studies at Oregon State University in Corvallis, Ore. She also is an ordained Baptist minister and holds master's and doctoral degrees from Southern Baptist Theological Seminary.\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9672006809237971, \"rank\": 0.03391159605118162, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 4470, \"end\": 4479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\", \"score\": 0.9999999695401134, \"rank\": 3.0458027804097826e-08, \"text\": \"Corvallis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corvallis_Knights\"}, {\"begin\": 4510, \"end\": 4517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 0.9790338702261326, \"rank\": 0.02140486000940716, \"text\": \"Baptist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}, {\"begin\": 4572, \"end\": 4588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"score\": 0.9999999998372004, \"rank\": 1.6259919219241794e-10, \"text\": \"Southern Baptist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Baptist_Convention\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"professor\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4400}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4409}, {\"ngram\": \"master's and doctoral degrees\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her most recent bookis Intersectional Theology: An Introductory Guide, co-authored with Grace Ji-Sun Kim.\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4699, \"end\": 4715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Ji-Sun